word_mean_info__list.difference: 主要指13岁到19岁之间的青少年，强调这个年龄段的人的本身特点。
现在几乎专指男青年，尤指10多岁到20多一点的男青年，但作为集合名时间男女青年都可指。
指青少年，系法律上的常用词。

bilingual.source: He used to be a very quiet teenager.
bilingual.target: 他过去是一个非常安静的青少年。

bilingual.source: American Teenager magazine asked her about her habits.
bilingual.target: 《美国青少年》杂志询问了她的习惯。

bilingual.source: "I really enjoyed the game!" exclaimed the teenager.

bilingual.source: Almost every teenager dreams of having the opportunity to sing in public.
bilingual.target: 几乎每个青少年都梦想有机会在公众面前唱歌。

bilingual.source: He often felt misunderstood as a teenager.

list.abstract: teenager（英 [ˈtiːneɪdʒə]，美 [ˈtiːneɪdʒər]），英语单词，作名词，指13至19岁之间的青少年男女。例句为When I was a teenager, I never learned how to save money.（当我十几岁的时候，我从来没有学会如何省钱。）。 词根：teen。
《Teenager》是美籍流行乐男歌手Samuel演唱的一首歌曲，由王雅君、勇敢的兄弟、2CHAMP作词，勇敢的兄弟、2CHAMP作曲，于2018年10月16日发行。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm a teenager. I'm in high school, I have rights, and it's time that I said so.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是个青少年。我上高中了，我有权利，现在就是我反抗的时间。

yingyinNormal.en: She stood up to them and became the first teenager ever to be nominated for a nobel peace prize.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她勇敢地与之对抗，并成为第一个获得诺贝尔和平奖提名的青少年。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, Tessa, I trusted you. To what? Never have fun, take a risk, be a normal teenager, like you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 泰莎我一直很信任你有吗？你要我跟你一样？不享乐，不冒险，当个平凡的青少年？

yingyinNormal.en: A terrifying development today as a vehicle matching that of a missing San Jose teenager was discovered late last night underneath a Santa Cruz lake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天事情有了不好的进展，与一名来自圣何塞的青少年匹配的车辆昨夜发现沉于圣克鲁斯湖底。

yingyinNormal.en: What kind of teenager did you think I was? Slutty. Easy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你把我当年想成是哪种人了啊？淫荡。风骚。

yingyinNormal.en: Mom did. Mom always took care of everything. Mom was a mess, Missy was a dumb teenager. I had to look after both of 'em.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈啊。妈总是照顾好了一切。妈妈当时魂不守舍，米希是个中二少女。只能我来一肩挑起照顾她们的责任。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
